{
  "stem": "512.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She was by the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the Nazis only opened up for one person to be able to get out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They didn't open up the whole door, because they actually didn't want us to go out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she was the first one to be pushed out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this cattle car was very high.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She got herself all beaten up, jumping.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the field, you could see there were cattle in the pastures.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I thought to myself, this is it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No more, no more.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm going to stay.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not running.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They started pushing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I says, I'm not going to jump.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I want to be killed right here already, among here, already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Many of them that were killed died in the, in the cattle car.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But she was so hysterical, standing there outside for me that people pushed me out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They grabbed me and pushed me out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the bombs were falling all over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Lost a lot of girls at that time, maybe half, maybe a little less.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it was a peculiar thing, as if God had it that way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Mothers and daughters, sisters together, perished together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, anyhow, after the bombing, after quite a while, the bombing had stopped.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The Nazis were kind enough that for the wounded, for the badly wounded, they gave an extra piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were so starved already that we were grabbing it from those, from those that couldn't handle it anymore anyhow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Half bloody, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We ate it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it became evening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It got dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They lined us up again, back in the, in the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
